OL,3,CTyne and Wear Metro control room's
OL,4,C1990s technology to be replaced
OL,6,FThe Tyne and Wear Metro has announced
OL,7,Fan #8.8 million project that will see
OL,8,F1990s technology updated in its
OL,9,Fcontrol room.
OL,11,FThe day-to-day operation of the Metro
OL,12,Fis done in the control room using the
OL,13,Fits Supervisory Control and Data
OL,14,FAcquisition System - known as SCADA -
OL,15,Fwhich will now be replaced with new
OL,16,Fdigital equipment.
