OL,3,CTyne and Wear Metro control room's
OL,4,C1990s technology to be replaced
OL,6,FIt will be the most significant
OL,7,Fupgrade to the Metro control room
OL,8,Fsince the installation of a #12million
OL,9,Fcomputerised signalling control system
OL,10,Fin 2018.
OL,12,FStuart Clarke, metro infrastructure
OL,13,Fdirector, said: "This project
OL,14,Frepresents a major investment in new
OL,15,Ftechnology for the Metro control room.
OL,17,F"The new system will allow us to
OL,18,Fresolve infrastructure issue more
OL,19,Feffectively, which will mean less
OL,20,Fdisruption for our customers.
