OL,3,CTyne and Wear Metro control room's
OL,4,C1990s technology to be replaced
OL,6,F"We're going to install a completely
OL,7,Fnew system, which brings with it the
OL,8,Fvery latest railway industry
OL,9,Ftechnology. It will replace a now life
OL,10,Fexpired system which was fitted in the
OL,11,F1990s.
OL,13,F"High voltage power is what makes the
OL,14,FMetro run. It's a vital system for us
OL,15,Fand one that we are investing in to
OL,16,Fensure we have Metro system for many
OL,17,Fmore years to come."
OL,19,FThe project is expected to take two
OL,20,Fyears to complete.
